# Unicode.GeneralCategory.unassigned

**Case**

A reserved unassigned code point or a non-character.

## Declaration

```swift
case unassigned
```

## Discussion

This value corresponds to the category `Unassigned` (abbreviated `Cn`) in the [https://unicode.org/reports/tr44/#General_Category_Values].
